    I think I am proud of the way that I handled the user flow by making sure that there were navigation bars and roots back and forth between different views.
c.	What was the most challenging aspect of this Achievement? 
    The most challenging part was the deployment of the application, it took me a while to try and deploy the app but to no avail.
d.	Did this Achievement meet your expectations? Did it give you the confidence to start working with your new Django skills?
    This achievement did meet my expectations I think I will be able to start working with Django but when I would deploy I will use a different deployment framework.